# MysticEast Project Rules

## Superpower Skills - MANDATORY

All work on this project MUST apply the following Superpower Skills:

### 1. Content Superpower
- Translate Eastern concepts into Western wellness language
- Use "Elemental Blueprint" not "BaZi Chart"
- Use "Core Element" not "Day Master"
- Focus on empowerment, not fortune-telling
- Action-oriented copy with clear CTAs

### 2. Design Superpower  
- Fusion aesthetic: Eastern ink wash + Western crystal wellness
- Colors: Indigo #2D1B4E, Gold #C9A227, Jade #00A86B
- Fonts: Cormorant Garamond (headings), Inter (body)
- Mobile-first, conversion-focused layouts

### 3. UX Superpower
- Every page must guide to free calculator or email capture
- Trust signals: privacy focus, no credit card required
- Beta phase: No pricing displayed

### 4. Code Superpower
- TypeScript strict mode
- Reusable components only
- Accessible, performant code

## Before Committing
- [ ] Content follows Superpower guidelines?
- [ ] Design matches Fusion aesthetic?
- [ ] Mobile responsive?
- [ ] Performance optimized?

## Beta Phase Rules
- NO pricing on any page
- Email contact: bazirili@foxmail.com
- Free calculator as primary CTA
- Emphasize "experience phase" messaging
